			<antipaladinauraofcowardice_3>
				<level type="number">3</level>
				<name type="string">Aura of the Grave (Su)</name>
				<text type="formattedtext">
					<p>At 3rd level, a seal-breaker is constantly surrounded by the chill of death. Mindless undead within 10 feet of the seal-breaker will not attack him unless directly ordered to, and even then only after succeeding at a Will save (DC = 10 + 1/2 the seal-breaker&#146;s level + his Charisma modifier). This ability replaces aura of cowardice.</p>
