			<antipaladinauraofvengeance_11>
				<level type="number">11</level>
				<name type="string">Aura of Rebirth (Su)</name>
				<text type="formattedtext">
					<p>At 11th level, if a living creature is slain within 10 feet of the seal-breaker, the seal-breaker can spend two uses of his smite good ability at the start of his next turn as a standard action to summon the spirit of a dead murderer to reanimate the corpse as a mohrg. The mohrg immediately rises and attacks the seal breaker&#146;s foes, acting under the antipaladin&#146;s command. After 1 minute, the murderer&#146;s soul leaves the body, which collapses, again lifeless. At 15th level, the seal-breaker can activate this ability as a move action. At 19th level, he can activate this ability as a swift action. This ability replaces aura of vengeance.</p>
