				<level type="number">17</level>
				<name type="string">Aura of depravity</name>
				<text type="formattedtext">
					<p>At 17th level, an antipaladin gains DR 5/good. Each enemy within 10 feet takes a -4 penalty on saving throws against compulsion effects. This ability functions only while the antipaladin is conscious, not if he is unconscious or dead.</p>
				</text>
			</antipaladinauraofdepravity_17>
			<antipaladinauraofdespair_8>
